---
---

<div
  style="background: #0B1A2E; border: 1px solid rgba(196, 154, 43, 0.2); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);"
>
  <!-- Window chrome -->
  <div
    style="background: rgba(29, 53, 87, 0.6); padding: 0.75rem 1rem; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196, 154, 43, 0.1);"
  >
    <span
      style="width: 12px; height: 12px; background: #FF5F57; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block;"
    ></span>
    <span
      style="width: 12px; height: 12px; background: #FFBD2E; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block;"
    ></span>
    <span
      style="width: 12px; height: 12px; background: #28C840; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block;"
    ></span>
    <span
      style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(139,156,175,0.5); margin-left: 0.5rem;"
      >zsh — ~/projects/my-app</span
    >
  </div>

  <!-- Terminal content -->
  <div class="terminal-body" style="padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.9; overflow-x: auto;">
    <!-- Command -->
    <div style="color: rgba(139,156,175,0.45);"># describe what you want built</div>
    <div>
      <span style="color: #C49A2B;">$</span>
      <span style="color: #E0BC5A;"> tmonier run "add OAuth2 login flow"</span>
    </div>
    <!-- Output lines -->
    <div style="color: #8B9CAF;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> drafting technical spec…
    </div>
    <div style="color: #8B9CAF;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> mapping tradeoffs, boundaries, contracts
    </div>
    <!-- Blank line -->
    <div style="height: 0.5rem;"></div>
    <!-- Spec approval -->
    <div style="color: #FFBD2E;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> spec ready — waiting for your approval
    </div>
    <div>
      <span style="color: #28C840;">▸ ✓</span>
      <span style="color: #8B9CAF;"> approved — decomposing into 3 parallel tasks</span>
    </div>
    <!-- Blank line -->
    <div style="height: 0.5rem;"></div>
    <!-- Parallel agents -->
    <div style="color: rgba(139,156,175,0.45);"># 3 agents launch in parallel</div>
    <div style="color: #8B9CAF;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> agent-1 → <span style="color: #E0BC5A;">worktree/auth</span> — OAuth2 provider
    </div>
    <div style="color: #8B9CAF;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> agent-2 → <span style="color: #E0BC5A;">worktree/gateway</span> — API gateway routes
    </div>
    <div style="color: #8B9CAF;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> agent-3 → <span style="color: #E0BC5A;">worktree/tests</span> — integration tests
    </div>
    <!-- Blank line -->
    <div style="height: 0.5rem;"></div>
    <!-- Cross-agent check -->
    <div style="color: #FFBD2E;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> ⚠ agent-2 modified auth.ts — conflict with agent-1's contract
    </div>
    <div style="color: #8B9CAF;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> awaiting your decision…
    </div>
    <div>
      <span style="color: #28C840;">▸ ✓</span>
      <span style="color: #8B9CAF;"> resolved — agent-2 aligned to agent-1's interface</span>
    </div>
    <!-- Blank line -->
    <div style="height: 0.5rem;"></div>
    <!-- Merge -->
    <div style="color: rgba(139,156,175,0.45);"># all agents done — review</div>
    <div style="color: #8B9CAF;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> 3 worktrees → 1 unified diff (847 lines)
    </div>
    <div style="color: #8B9CAF;">
      <span style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6);">▸</span> architectural consistency: <span style="color: #28C840;">pass</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span style="color: #28C840;">▸ ✓</span>
      <span style="color: #8B9CAF;"> merged to main — feature complete</span>
    </div>
    <!-- Cursor -->
    <div style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <span style="color: #C49A2B;">$</span>
      <span
        style="display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 1.1em; background: #C49A2B; margin-left: 4px; vertical-align: text-bottom; animation: blink 1.2s step-end infinite;"
      ></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  @keyframes blink {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .terminal-body {
      font-size: 0.65rem !important;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem !important;
      line-height: 1.75 !important;
    }
  }
</style>
